issue.title: Configuring Perspectives for Truck Owners & Non-Truck Owners
issue.body:
- Where we have the different user stories determined and built for the truck owners and non-truck owners

Such as: 

- Truck owner has slightly different sign up screen, update menu, update location, etc. 

-Non-Truck owner has different sign up screen, save favorites (list of food trucks), see locations of food trucks.
